We are also sending teams to Darjeeling and Kalimpong ( in West Bengal )," he said . Two districts -- West and South -- in Sikkim remained inaccessible to the army , delaying rescue work , he said , adding that the local authorities were carrying out relief work and army commanders stationed there have been alerted . The casualties have occurred mostly in the North District and in towns and villages like Rangpo , Dikchu , Singtam and Chungthang located along the course of Teesta river , officials said .